data.description: Welcome home to 42350 Forest Oaks Dr. in Elizabeth, CO. Who wouldn't love driving home every day to the beautifully and scenic Spring Valley Ranch Golf Community. This home sits on a 1/3 of an acre lot with gorgeous, matured trees providing lots of privacy in your backyard oasis. Step inside and you will find a well-maintained 4bed, 3 bath home accompanied by tall ceilings and beaming natural light throughout.  The main level features a formal dining, open concept living room and kitchen with the cozy gas fireplace. A true chefs delight with gorgeous cherry cabinets, double oven, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and island featuring an abundance of cabinet space. The small details make a difference please note; the pull-out drawers in the base cabinets for convenience of storing your pots and pans, a main floor bedroom or office, heated garage, to the convenience of the upper-level laundry room with utility sink. On the upper level you will find a generous sized primary bedroom with lots of windows, en-suite 5-piece bath with soaking tub and a massive walk-in closet. Two additional- nice sized bedrooms with a jack-n-jill full bath.  The grand sized loft gives endless opportunities to host an additional office, work-out space, kids play area or the perfect place to land for movie nights! Be sure to step out the backyard to see the size of the private yard, the gorgeous pine trees, and imagine sitting by the firepit roasting marshmallows in the summer evenings! The unfinished basement is ready for your personal touches for additional living space. Great community, close to many amenities in Elizabeth and surrounding areas with east access to DIA, town of Parker and Denver.
